metadata.name: Peony Sylph
metadata.description:
The first of my Blooming Sylph collection, hand drawn on Clip Studio Paint. This is also my very first artwork on this platform, and I am looking forward to creating more content and to meet more like-minded artists and curators of art.

1897 x 1600px
300dpi

The layered file will be provided to the first owner of this work.
